This is a custom distribution of FreeType, version 2.4.9, with a XMake-based build
system.

The original README file of FreeType is at 'docs/FreeType-Readme'.


License
-------

FreeType's license is unchanged: this library is free software; you can redistribute
it and/or modify it under the terms of either the 'FreeType License' or the 'GNU General
Public License  version 2'. See the file 'docs/License.txt' for the details.


Submodules
----------

This distribution use XMake as a GIT submodule. To download it, do:

	$ git submodule init
	$ git submodule update


Compilation
-----------

It is recommended to compile the library in a separate folder. Here's how I do it:

	$ mkdir build
	$ cd build
	$ cmake ..
	$ make
